author=InterAct
description=<p>These codes change the description, value, and power of the item in the slot. For example, an Adamantine Dagger is better than a Worn Dagger.</p> F1 - Serrated
F0 - Oak
F3 - Serrated Oak
F2 - Darkwood
F5 - Serrated Darkwood
F4 - Oak Darkwood
F7 - Serrated Oak Darkwood
08 - Adamantine
0B - Serrated Adamantine
0A - Mythril
0D - Serrated Mythril
0C - Adamntine Mythril
0F - Serrated Adamantine Mythril
0E - Worn
06 - Rusty
patch=1,EE,C06D7DC9,extended,1CDE2FEB

